title: NobunagaVerse
description: A college student - a descendant of famous historical warlord Nobunaga Oda - is dragged into the battles of a female Nobunaga Oda from a parallel universe only to find out that there are in fact a total of 986 alternative versions of Nobunaga Oda, all who he's now trying to protect.
author: Antai, Zeami
